        function sortTable(n, table) {
            var table, rows, switching, i, x, y, shouldSwitch, dir, switchcount = 0;
            table = document.getElementById(table);
            switching = true;
            dir = "asc";
            while (switching) {
                switching = false;
                rows = table.getElementsByTagName("tr");
                for (i = 1; i < (rows.length - 1); i++) {
                    shouldSwitch = false;
                    x = rows[i].getElementsByTagName("th")[n];
                    y = rows[i + 1].getElementsByTagName("th")[n];
                    if (dir == "asc") {
                        if (!isNaN(parseInt(x.innerHTML.toLowerCase()))) {
                            if (parseInt(x.innerHTML.toLowerCase()) > parseInt(y.innerHTML.toLowerCase())) {
                                shouldSwitch = true;
                                break;
                            }
                        } else {
                            if (x.innerHTML.toLowerCase() > y.innerHTML.toLowerCase()) {
                                shouldSwitch = true;
                                break;
                            }
                        }
                    } else if (dir == "desc") {
                        if (!isNaN(parseInt(x.innerHTML.toLowerCase()))) {
                            if (parseInt(x.innerHTML.toLowerCase()) < parseInt(y.innerHTML.toLowerCase())) {
                                shouldSwitch = true;
                                break;
                            }
                        } else {
                            if (x.innerHTML.toLowerCase() < y.innerHTML.toLowerCase()) {
                                shouldSwitch = true;
                                break;
                            }
                        }
                    }
                }
                if (shouldSwitch) {
                    rows[i].parentNode.insertBefore(rows[i + 1], rows[i]);
                    switching = true;

                    switchcount++;
                } else {
                    if (switchcount == 0 && dir == "asc") {
                        dir = "desc";
                        switching = true;
                    }
                }
            }
        }

        function getStreetAbrvs(type){
            for(var street in street_types){

            }

            return null;

        function jigAddress(selector) {
            var types = ["Apt", "Suite", "Room"];
            var suffixes = ["A", "B", "C", "1", "2", "3"];

            var street = $(selector).val().split(',');
            if(street.length > 1) street.splice(-1, 1);
            var split = street.join(',').split(' ');

            jigged = false;
            for(var i in split){
                var street = getStreetAbrvs(split[i]);
                if(street_types[street] != null){
                    var abbr = street_types[street].abbrs.shift();
                    street_types[street].abbrs.push(abbr);

                    var type = types[Math.floor(Math.random() * types.length)];
                    var suffix = suffixes[Math.floor(Math.random() * suffixes.length)];
                    split[i] = `${abbr[0]}${abbr.substr(1).toLowerCase()}, ${type} ${suffix}`;      
                    jigged = true;
                }
            }

            if(jigged)
                $(selector).val(split.join(' '));
        }

        function formatDate(date) {
            var hours = date.getHours();
            var minutes = date.getMinutes();
            var seconds = date.getSeconds();
            var ampm = hours >= 12 ? 'PM' : 'AM';
            var day = date.getUTCDate().toString();
            var month = (date.getUTCMonth() + 1) < 10 ? '0' + (date.getUTCMonth() + 1).toString() : (date.getUTCMonth() + 1).toString();
            var year = date.getUTCFullYear().toString();
            hours = hours % 12;
            hours = hours ? hours : 12; // the hour '0' should be '12'
            hours = hours < 10 ? '0' + hours : hours;
            minutes = minutes < 10 ? '0' + minutes : minutes;
            seconds = seconds < 10 ? '0' + seconds : seconds;
            var strTime = day + "/" + month + "/" + year + "T" + hours + ':' + minutes + ':' + seconds + ' ' + ampm;
            return strTime;
        }

        function cc_format(value) {
            var v = value.replace(/\s+/g, '').replace(/[^0-9]/gi, '');
            var matches = v.match(/\d{4,16}/g);
            var match = matches && matches[0] || '';
            var parts = [];
            for (i = 0, len = match.length; i < len; i += 4) {
                parts.push(match.substring(i, i + 4))
            }
            if (parts.length) {
                return parts.join(' ')
            } else {
                return value
            }
        }

            if ($("#test-site option:selected").text() == "Custom") {
                swal({
                        title: 'Set custom site',
                        content: {
                            element: "input",
                            attributes: {
                                placeholder: "Input link",
                            }
                        },
                        button: {
                            text: "Set",
                        },
                    })
                    .then(link => {
                        if (link) {
                            $("#test-site option:selected").val(link);
                        }
                    })
            }
        })

        function testWebhook() {
            if ($("#webhook").val().includes("https://discordapp.com/api/webhooks/") || $("#webhook").val().includes("https://hooks.slack.com/services/")) {
                swal("Testing webhook...", "\n", "info", {
                    buttons: {
                        visible: false
                    },
                    closeOnClickOutside: false,
                    timer: 4000
                });
                var json = '{ "username": "CyberAIO", "icon_url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/422926053745623040/437275593571172362/logo.png", "attachments":[{ "title": "Webhook Test", "color": "#0000FF", "footer": "CyberAIO Success Logger" }] }';
                xhr = new XMLHttpRequest();
                var url = $("#webhook").val().includes("discord") ? $("#webhook").val().replace("/slack", "") + "/slack" : $("#webhook").val();
                xhr.open("POST", url, true);
                xhr.setRequestHeader("Content-type", "application/json");
                xhr.onreadystatechange = function() {
                    if (xhr.readyState == 4) {
                        swal("Success", "A test message was sent to the specified webhook!", "success", {
                            timer: 3000
                        });
                    }
                }
                var data = json;
                xhr.send(data);
            } else if ($("#webhook").val().replace(" ", "") == "") {
                swal("No webhook", "You don't have a webhook set!", "info", {
                    timer: 2500
                });
            } else {
                swal("Invalid webhook", "You seem to have entered an invalid webhook!", "warning", {
                    timer: 2500
                });
            }
        }
    </script>
